I want to talk to him alone

3
00:00:10.466 --> 00:00:14.800
You and I have no home. If you want to chat alone, I'll let you chat.

4
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:15.933
Didn't you eat?

5
00:00:15.933 --> 00:00:18.800
I've been waiting for you upstairs for a long time

6
00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:27.233
you

7
00:00:28.866 --> 00:00:30.033
Who is that?

8
00:00:32.533 --> 00:00:36.466
