11
00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:45.466
Want to kill me with your own hands

12
00:00:50.933 --> 00:00:52.500
Say something.

13
00:00:53.500 --> 00:00:54.366
Sorry.

14
00:00:55.333 --> 00:00:57.966
Dad has his own reasons

15
00:00:59.533 --> 00:01:02.166
You admit that you are my father

